N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 665.9 - Network access revenues

State Regulations
(a) Network
access revenues (accounts 5080-5084) shall include revenues derived from the
provision of exchange access services to an interexchange carrier or to an end
user of telecommunications services beyond the exchange carrier's
network. (b) Billing and
collections service provided under exchange access tariffs shall be included in
the Miscellaneous Revenues Group. Notes
